---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Škola hokeja - IHK Varaždin"
  description="Škola hokeja za djecu u IHK Varaždin. Treninzi tri puta tjedno ujutro. Profesionalni treneri i individualan pristup."
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Škola hokeja"
    subtitle="Program za djecu - mali broj polaznika, maksimalna pažnja!"
    backgroundImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621263958240-fab64819119b?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1074"
  />

  <!-- Hockey School Info -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">O školi hokeja</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Program počinje kao škola klizanja na ledu za početnike, s fokusom na razvoj osnovnih vještina klizanja.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Za napredne polaznike nudimo hokejaške elemente i tehnike, omogućujući im razvoj prema kompetitivnom hokeju.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-12">
              <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                      <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                      </svg>
                      <p class="text-primary-900 font-bold">
                          Škola hokeja održava se od 29.12. do 4.1.
                      </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-gray-700">
                      <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                      </svg>
                      <p class="font-medium">
                          3 termina dnevno od 8 do 11 sati - od početnika do naprednih
                      </p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefits -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Zašto škola hokeja?</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-800 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 4 stručna trenera s iskustvom rada s djecom</li>
                  <li>• 3 termina dnevno - od početnika do naprednih</li>
                  <li>• Rad u malim grupama za bolju edukaciju</li>
                  <li>• Jutarnji termini od 8 do 11 sati</li>
                  <li>• Siguran i kontroliran okoliš za učenje</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Što djeca uče?</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-800 space-y-1">
                  <li>• Osnovne vještine klizanja na ledu</li>
                  <li>• Pravilno držanje palice i šuta</li>
                  <li>• Timski rad i sportski duh</li>
                  <li>• Fizičku kondiciju i koordinaciju</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 md:p-6 rounded mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-1">Napomena</h4>
              <p class="text-blue-800">
                Treninzi se održavaju u Klizalištu Varaždin. Za više informacija o upisu, cijenama i raspoloživim mjestima kontaktirajte nas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-blue-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Zainteresirani ste za školu hokeja?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Kontaktirajte nas za više informacija o upisu, raspoloživim mjestima i cijenama!
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors"
        >
          Kontaktiraj nas
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
